quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,Si kammu on fettii
  82,2,Si koode …óe cariima
  82,3,Si maaje …óe puccitaama
  82,4,Si genaale mbaylaama
  82,5,Fittaandu annda kondu wa…óno e golle e kondu leelnuno e golle
  82,6,Eehey ma ne…ó…óanke hol ko hoomtuma e joom ma Teddu…ì…óo O
  82,7,Oon tak…óo ma O fotndi ter…ó ma O wa…ó ma potandir…óo
  82,8,E kala mbaadi ndi O haaja O feewnir ma
  82,9,"Alah, woni ko on yeddoo…ìe √±alngu no…ìdi"
  82,10,Pellet ina woodi e dow mon malaykaaji deenooji
  82,11,Teddu…ói binndooji
  82,12,Ganndu…ói ko ngolloton
  82,13,Pellet …ìeen …óiggu…ìe ho…ìe e neema
  82,14,Faajiree…ìe noon ina e yiite
  82,15,Ho…ìe naatange √±ande √±alngu njo…ìdi
  82,16,…ìe ngonah wirnatoo…ìe nge haa bada
  82,17,Holko anndin ma √±alngu njobdi
  82,18,Refti holko anndin ma √±alngu njobdi
  82,19,√±ande fittaandu jogantaaki fittaandu hay huunde huunde fof ko Alla woodani √±ande heen
  83,1,Halkaare woodanii …ìeen ustoo…ìe peese
  83,2,…ìeen peesnatoo…ìe yim…ìe …ìe …óa…ì…ìa timminaneede
  83,3,Si…ìe …ìetanii …ìe wolla …ìe peesanii …ìe usta
  83,4,E …ìee kan fellitaa wonnde ko …ìe immintintee…ìe
  83,5,Woodanii mbo √±alngu mawngu
  83,6,√±ande yim…ìe ummanii jom binnde
